<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287269>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Pseudoceros juani sp. nov. (MNRJ-PLAT 40) A. in vivo; B. P. juani ventral view; C. detail of the anterior region; D. sagital section of female reproductive structures; E. sagittal section of the male reproductive structures, showing prostatic vesicle; F. sagittal section of male reproductive structures; G. Pseudoceros juani in situ. Photo: L. F. Cassino. ce: cerebral eyespots; cg: cement glands; cp: cement pouch; du: uterine duct; fa: female atrium; fg: female gonopore; it: main intestine; ma: male atrium; mg: male gonopore; pe: pseudotentacular eyespots; ph: pharynx; pv: prostatic vesicle; pt: pseudotentacle; ra: rhabdites; sd: seminal duct; st: stylet; su: sucker; sv: seminal vesicle; va: vagina; vs: vas deferens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287269/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287267>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Pseudoceros rawlinsonae (MNRJ-PLAT 01). A. in vivo; B. ventral view; C. detail of ventral view; D. detail from the anterior region, showing cerebral eyespots; E. detail from the anterior region showing tentacular eyespots; F. detail from the anterior ventral region; G. sagital section of the specimen body; H. sagittal section of male reproductive structures; I. sagittal section of female reproductive structures. ce: cerebral eyespots; cg: cement glands; cp: cement pouch; ep: epidermis; fg: female gonopore; it: main intestine; ma: male atrium; mg: male gonopore; ml: muscular layer; ph: pharynx; pt: pseudotentacles; pv: prostatic vesicle; ra: rhabdites; st: stylet; su: sucker; sv: seminal vesicle; te: tentacular eyespots; ut: uteri; va: vagina; vd: vas deferens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287267/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

